Usage: [options] input-file output-file
Options:
  -?, --help                   Display this help message
  -v, --version                Display the version
  -e, --encode                 Encode WAV -> BRR
  -d, --decode                 Decode BRR -> WAV
  -t, --transcode              Transcode WAV -> (BRR) -> WAV
  -l, --loop-start             Set the loop start sample
  -p, --pitch                  Set the pitch rate for decoding
  -g, --enable-gauss           Enable gaussian filtering during decoding